Class Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.users.model.Contact
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Contact
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A Contact represents information that can be used to contact a human being and information relevant to business contact with the human being.
